sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant You
  participant GitHub
  participant Jenkins
  participant DockerHub
  participant Terraform
  participant AWS as AWS EC2 App Host
  participant Ansible
  participant App as App Container

  You->>Jenkins: Start pipeline with parameters
  GitHub-->>Jenkins: Provide repository source
  Jenkins->>Jenkins: Validate stack, npm ci, lint, build
  Jenkins->>Jenkins: Build image with Supabase build args
  Jenkins->>DockerHub: Push image tag and latest

  loop For each target environment
    Jenkins->>Terraform: init, validate, plan
    alt APPLY_INFRA is true
      Terraform-->>AWS: create or update VPC subnet SG EC2
      Jenkins->>Terraform: read app_public_ip and ssh_user
      Jenkins->>Jenkins: generate ansible hosts.generated.yml
    else APPLY_INFRA is false
      Jenkins->>Terraform: try reading existing outputs
    end

    Jenkins->>Ansible: run provision.yml
    alt ROLLBACK_DEPLOY is true
      Jenkins->>Ansible: run rollback.yml with ROLLBACK_TAG
    else ROLLBACK_DEPLOY is false
      Jenkins->>Ansible: run deploy.yml with APP_IMAGE_TAG
    end

    Ansible->>AWS: docker pull and docker run
    AWS->>App: start container on port 3000
    Jenkins->>App: GET /api/health
    App-->>Jenkins: 200 OK
  end

  Jenkins-->>You: Build success with image tag
